data.description: Welcome to your serene retreat in Four Oaks! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom ranch home sits on a spacious 0.61 acre lot just outside the city limits, offering tranquility and convenience. With an open floor plan, a screened-in back porch, and a fully wired workshop in the backyard, this property provides ample space for relaxation and recreation. Enjoy the convenience of easy access to I-95, I-40, and Raleigh while embracing the freedom of no HOA!
